      <div>
        <h2 class="font-headline font-bold text-xl text-on-surface mb-3">2. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p class="mb-2">We collect information you provide directly to us, including:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-2">
          <li>Name, email address, and phone number (provided during purchase or inquiry)</li>
          <li>Payment transaction references (we do not store card numbers or bank credentials)</li>
          <li>Course or product preferences</li>
          <li>Messages sent through our contact or inquiry forms</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-2">We may also automatically collect limited technical data such as browser type and pages visited for analytics purposes.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-headline font-bold text-xl text-on-surface mb-3">3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p class="mb-2">We use the information we collect to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-2">
          <li>Process your purchase and deliver digital products</li>
          <li>Generate and send GST invoices</li>
          <li>Respond to inquiries and provide customer support</li>
          <li>Send purchase confirmation and relevant product updates</li>
          <li>Improve our website and services</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-2">We do not sell, rent, or trade your personal information to third parties for marketing purposes.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-headline font-bold text-xl text-on-surface mb-3">4. Payment Information</h2>
        <p>All payment transactions are handled by Razorpay, a secure and PCI-DSS compliant payment gateway. FullOnBaan does not store any card details, bank account numbers, or payment credentials. For Razorpay's data practices, please refer to <a href="https://razorpay.com/privacy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-primary hover:underline">Razorpay's Privacy Policy</a>.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-headline font-bold text-xl text-on-surface mb-3">5. Data Sharing</h2>
        <p>We may share your information with trusted third-party services strictly necessary for operating our business (e.g., email delivery via EmailJS, payment processing via Razorpay). These parties are contractually obligated to keep your data secure and use it only for the specified purpose.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-headline font-bold text-xl text-on-surface mb-3">6. Data Retention</h2>
        <p>We retain your personal information only as long as necessary to fulfil the purposes described in this policy, comply with legal obligations (such as GST record-keeping), and resolve any disputes. Purchase records are retained for a minimum of 7 years as required under Indian tax law.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-headline font-bold text-xl text-on-surface mb-3">7. Cookies</h2>
        <p>Our website may use essential cookies for core functionality. We do not use tracking or advertising cookies. By using our site, you consent to the use of essential cookies only.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-headline font-bold text-xl text-on-surface mb-3">8. Your Rights</h2>
        <p>You have the right to access, correct, or request deletion of your personal data (subject to legal retention requirements). To exercise these rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:fullonbaan@gmail.com" class="text-primary hover:underline">fullonbaan@gmail.com</a>.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
